full_text: Great thread for non-fluffy, worthwhile reads: https://t.co/H0IpBmByRQ

But I love watching the tweets of a few geniuses on here. Piecing together their schema of the world is where it's at for me. Never about the specific issues.

I'm so* cynical when I'm tired. I should stay off Instagram.
